{"id":636112,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/象甲书店-学校网课直播屡遭封禁，我们的互联网/","date":"2020-02-19T07:32:36Z","modified":"2020-02-19T07:32:36Z","title":"象甲书店 | 学校网课直播屡遭封禁，我们的互联网有病","content":"<p>CDT编者按：本文公众号原文已被删除</p>\n<p>原创：象甲</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636114\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病-174x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"862\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病-174x300.png 174w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病-594x1024.png 594w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病-768x1324.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病-891x1536.png 891w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病-1080x1863.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病.png 1122w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>受疫情影响，从幼儿园到大学，国内的各个学校都推迟开学，纷纷开始了网络授课。</p>\n<p>教育是立国之本，疫情期间利用互联网授课，本来也是一件严肃的事情，但是由于国内互联网敏感词的泛滥，各大学校网络授课或者网络直播授课，都遭受了课件被屏蔽、直播间被封禁等尴尬的局面。</p>\n<p>国家教育部钦定的教学内容，怎么在网上就成为了遭受屏蔽和封禁的对象？</p>\n<p>首先遭受封禁的是医学生理课，多个人体器官名词成为网络敏感词。一位医学护理专业的老师抱怨，她在QQ上讲课，几秒钟就被封了，原因是涉黄。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636115\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病2-15-300x130.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"217\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病2-15-300x130.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病2-15-1024x445.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病2-15-768x334.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病2-15-1536x668.png 1536w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病2-15-2048x891.png 2048w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病2-15-1080x470.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>生物课也成为重灾区，这是瑞安中学的高二生物网课直播间被封，也是因为涉嫌传播淫秽色情信息。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636116\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病3-11-222x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"676\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病3-11-222x300.png 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病3-11-757x1024.png 757w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病3-11-768x1039.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病3-11.png 996w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>政治课也不能幸免，这是抖音平台上透露的一个案例：政治老师上课涉嫌政治话题，直播间被封。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636117\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11-170x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"883\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11-170x300.png 170w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11-580x1024.png 580w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11-768x1356.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11-870x1536.png 870w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11-1160x2048.png 1160w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11-1080x1907.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病4-11.png 1223w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>紧跟其后，是历史课的小心翼翼。然而，仍然难以避免直播授课被封。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636118\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病5-7-208x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病5-7-208x300.png 208w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病5-7-711x1024.png 711w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病5-7-768x1106.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病5-7-1067x1536.png 1067w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病5-7-1423x2048.png 1423w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病5-7-1080x1555.png 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>语文课本里的鲁迅已经基本全退出了，应该讲比较安全了吧，但是仍然不行：语文课老师讲解的内容，在QQ群里被屏蔽。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636119\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病6-7-169x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病6-7-169x300.png 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病6-7-576x1024.png 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病6-7-768x1365.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病6-7-864x1536.png 864w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病6-7-1080x1920.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病6-7.png 1125w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>比较来看，英语课相对最安全，毕竟英语对于网管来说是一道语言门槛。然而，英语课直播也出现了被封的现象。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636120\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6-201x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"745\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6-201x300.png 201w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6-687x1024.png 687w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6-768x1144.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6-1031x1536.png 1031w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6-1375x2048.png 1375w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6-1080x1609.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病7-6.png 1432w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>目前看起来，最安全的只有网上体育课，不会涉及到敏感内容。但是，有学校组织线上的升旗仪式，照样被封。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636121\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病8-4-226x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"663\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病8-4-226x300.png 226w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病8-4-772x1024.png 772w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病8-4-768x1019.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病8-4-1080x1433.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病8-4.png 1096w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>去微博上略略一看，网课话题下面是一堆网友在反应，上网课遭受了被封禁的局面。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636122\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病9-5-191x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"784\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病9-5-191x300.png 191w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病9-5-653x1024.png 653w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病9-5-768x1204.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病9-5-980x1536.png 980w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病9-5-1080x1693.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/有病9-5.png 1116w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>学生们在网课遭受封禁面前嘻嘻哈哈，授课老师则是小心翼翼相互提醒，严肃媒体对网课遭封禁装聋作哑，自媒体则把它当成段子内容。</p>\n<p>国家教育部钦定的教学内容，居然成为了互联网上屏蔽和封禁的内容。如果没有这场疫情下大规模的网络授课，学生和老师们大概还不会如此直观地认知：</p>\n<p>我们的互联网病了。</p>\n<p>我们的互联网充斥着举报和敏感词，充斥着只能为之的错别字，正常的沟通和交流只能在这些禁锢之间寻找缝隙。</p>\n<p>更可怕的是，我们已经逐渐适应了这种有病的互联网，用越来越多的暗语和隐喻指代来做交流，把遭受封号删帖屏蔽封禁当成了日常。</p>\n<p>包括此刻，我们在小心翼翼地写这篇稿子。</p>\n<p>对于未来，我们深感担忧。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-636113\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-300x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-300x300.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-150x150.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-768x768.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-1080x1080.png 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-440x440.png 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1-50x50.png 50w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/图片-1.png 1250w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CDS档案 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/网络审查\">网络审查</a></strong></p>\n","author":1067,"categories":[18271,38912,38960],"tags":[8616,38892,14804,21926]}